trailingComments.value:
*
 * Pointwise Math.pow(x, y)
 * 
 * @export
 * @param {Number|Array} m1
 * @param {Number|Array} m2
 * @returns {Number|Array}
 * @example 
 * 
 * pow(1, 2)
 * // Equals Math.pow(1, 2)
 * pow([1, 2], [2, 2])
 * // Equals [Math.pow(1, 2), Math.pow(2, 2)]
 * pow([[2,1], [1,2]], [[2, 2], [2, 2]]))
 * // Equals [ [Math.pow(2, 2), Math.pow(1, 2)], [Math.pow(1, 2), Math.pow(2, 2)] ]

arguments.value: pow() requires two matrices having the same size
arguments.raw: 'pow() requires two matrices having the same size'
